# Setup ReactJS Project with Antd

	1. Start the project via `create-react-app`
		a. https://create-react-app.dev/docs/getting-started/
	2. Set up Eslint for React.js in VSCode
		a. https://medium.com/how-to-react/config-eslint-and-prettier-in-visual-studio-code-for-react-js-development-97bb2236b31a
		b. npm install eslint --save-dev
		c. npx eslint --init
		d. npm install eslint-config-prettier eslint-plugin-prettier prettier --save-dev
		    "editor.codeActionsOnSave": {
		        "source.fixAll.eslint": true
		    },
		    "editor.formatOnSave": true,
		    "eslint.alwaysShowStatus": true,
		    "files.autoSave": "onFocusChange"
	3. Setup Antd
		a. npm install -s antd
		b. npm install --save @ant-design/icons
		c. https://ant.design/docs/react/use-with-create-react-app
		d. npm install --save @craco/craco
		e. npm install --save craco-less
